description:
Application under Section 73 of the Town and country Planning Act 1990 for variation of conditions 15 (BREEAM) and 21 (Biodiversity Plan) to have the effect of varying the requirements of the timing of the submission of details; and for variation of condition 2 (Approved Documents and Plans) to have the effect to considering minor material amendments of the planning permission ref: P092024 granted on 15 April 2010.  The minor material amendments to include:

•  Level 0: Increase the size of changing room 1 resulting in the footprint extending by 1.8m to south;
•  Level 0: Additional doors to plant space adjacent to stair 7 along west elevation;`
•  Levels 1, 1A, 2, 2A, 3: Stair 2 facing Rodney Street squared off to provide uniform envelope with associated elevation and window size and position changes;
•  Level 2: Redesign of roof lights of sports hall at piazza from two rectangular roof lights to 12 smaller flush (walkover) roof lights and four smaller feature roof lights with associated seating to their perimeter.  The pergola to the Piazza removed;
•  Level 3: Increase in the size of the Canopy over Stair 10;
•  Level 5: Removal of terrace to northwest corner by incorporating area as part of staffroom (increased by 11sq m), with associated elevation and window size and position changes;
•  Roof Plan: Redesign of Level 5 roof with cutback of overhang;
•  Roof Plan: Addition of roof guarding to roof areas of levels 2, 3, 4, and an lightweight external ladder to the east elevation of level 5, and guardrails to roof areas of levels 1, 2A and 5;
•  Roof Plan: Addition of roof plant and with associated louvers and vents on the Levels 2, 3, 4 and 5 roofs;
•  Position and size amendments to the windows and doors to all the elevations of the proposed building;
•  Amendments to the junctions and relationship between facing materials;
•  Removal of one of the 11 trees in Group 47 along Rodney Street, and replacement tree provided as part of the landscaping work
